---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHero from '../../components/PageHero.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="The Design" description="How TVC's land is laid out — the wildlife corridor, food forests, cultivated zones, and water works — plus a drone flyover of the farm." image="/images/pages/home/hero.jpg">
  <PageHero
    eyebrow="Our Journey"
    title="The design"
    image="/images/pages/home/hero.jpg"
    imageAlt="Aerial view of the farm's layout, with housing clusters and zones labeled"
  />

  <section class="section wrapper">
    <p>The farm's regeneration follows permaculture and regenerative design principles: a wildlife corridor higher on the hill closer to the forest is left to grow by itself, food forests combine supporting plants with fruit-bearing trees, and the rest is actively cultivated. The last several years have been dedicated to land rejuvenation, letting vegetation grow in whatever form it takes.</p>
    <p>The farm's layout — the housing clusters, the food forest zones, the water works — is mapped out below.</p>
    <div class="map-embed">
      <iframe
        loading="lazy"
        src="https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/0/embed?mid=1b_d-2ZOwDBRTJjbDZ2ovJ7QsdPiqnYrA"
        width="640"
        height="480"
        style="border:0"
        title="TVC farm plans and design map"
      ></iframe>
    </div>

    <h3>Aerial view</h3>
    <p>A drone flight over the farm, showing the land, the food forest, and the surrounding hills from above.</p>
    <div class="video-embed">
      <iframe
        loading="lazy"
        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ixHNXOiQ9vM"
        title="TVC Aerial View"
        frameborder="0"
        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
        allowfullscreen
      ></iframe>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .map-embed iframe {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 640px;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
  }

  .video-embed {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 640px;
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
  }

  .video-embed iframe {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border: 0;
  }
</style>
